://webdevstudios.com/2015/05/15/webdevstudios-is-hiring/">WebDevStudios is hiring!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://webdevstudios.com">WebDevStudios.com</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:20:"Elizabeth Ehrenpreis";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2902:"<p>You read it right! The WebDevStudios and <a class="" href="http://maintainn.com">Maintainn</a> teams are continuing to expand, and we need YOUR help!</p>\n<p>Maybe you’ve gotten to know some of us through meeting us at events, through <a href="https://twitter.com/williamsba/lists/wds" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, through here on our blog, or heck, maybe you’ve worked with some of our folks through previous/independent collaborations. If we have had the pleasure of meeting, you already know that the folks on the WDS team are a rambunctious, hard-working, clever bunch (if we may say so ourselves), and we&#8217;re looking to add people to the mix.</p>\n<p><span id="more-11222"></span></p>\n<p>We are seeking folks to fill a variety of positions&#8211;front end and back end developers, as well as a project manager. Chris recently detailed <a href="http://webdevstudios.com/2015/05/13/day-life-dev-wds/">what the average day in the life of a WDS dev looks like</a>, too, if you&#8217;re curious!</p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t feel like you&#8217;re the right fit, please share the links; our community has incredible folk in it, and we know that YOU know good people. Send &#8217;em our way, please!</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-11226 size-full" src="http://3oil7x2swx3d30yjgq23wmyu.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/lightsaber.gif" alt="webdevstudios, hiring WordPress developers, developer jobs, dev jobs, tech jobs, " width="500" height="278" /></p>\n<p>We’re seeking <em><del>Jedis</del></em> folks with WordPress development experience (you might have guessed that one!) who are comfortable working remotely and ready to join an incredible team.</p>\n<p>Check out the links below for more details on the available positions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/jobs/front-end-developer/" target="_blank">WDS Front End Developer</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/jobs/wordpress-developer/" target="_blank">WDS Back End Developer</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/jobs/front-end-developer-maintainn/" target="_blank">Maintainn Front End Developer</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/jobs/project-manager/">Project Manager</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Grab your lightsaber, steel yourself, and join us!</p>\n<div id="attachment_11227" style="width: 509px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-11227 size-full" src="http://3oil7x2swx3d30yjgq23wmyu.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/turtlesaber.gif" alt="webdevstudios, hiring WordPress developers, developer jobs, dev jobs, tech jobs, " width="499" height="281" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Are you ready for this?!</p></div>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://webdevstudios.com/2015/05/15/webdevstudios-is-hiring/">WebDevStudios is hiring!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://webdevstudios.com">WebDevStudios.com</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"http://webdevstudios.com/2015/05/15/webdevstudios-is-hiring/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:""